Davram 41st lvl Magician of the Academy of Arcane Science</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ureegeraxehaft.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Reeger Axehaft</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/27/01 10:46:59 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Prince and King in Chardok</span><hr size=1> Hmm...Fire resist gear.  Prince is not so bad, we pulled him on accident, along with a couple other sarnaks, but we them down.  The King was a little more interesting, but we can take him down with not too many problems.  Both use an area effect fire attack that is not so nasty with the Prince, nasty with King, and from what I understand..devestating from the Queen.<br>
Oh, the hallway before the library room (the room with the stairs that go down and the locked door at the bottom) is considered a safe hallway.  There are only 2 mobs that spawn in there and they are at the one end.  The other end is good. <p>Reeger Axehaft <BR>
53rd Level Warrior <BR>
"Let me Axe you a question!"</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uadexxeda.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Adex Xeda</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://kilroyc.globalhelix.com/adex_icon.jpg height=30 width=30 BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>The Swift</BR>Steel Warrior Contributor</span><br>  Posts: 199<br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/28/01 8:59:12 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://kilroyc.globalhelix.com/adex_portrait.jpg width = 136 height = 267 ></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Prince and King in Chardok</span><hr size=1> HAHA Anadon you encountered what my guild affectionatly calls the 40-armed sarnak. <br>
<br>
Yes the very first time we tried the prince we aggroed the FD pull to. We fixed this by moving the raid down to the middle of the hallway past the corner you're tagging from.<br>
<br>
The safe spot is located,, hmm how do I describe.<br>
<br>
The prince room is off a donut-shaped hallway. If you exit the prince room and go to the exact opposite side of the donut hallway, you'll bump into a locked door. Opening this door yeilds a stairway that leads on to the library and herbalist rooms. The bottom of this stairway is a safe spot. No roamers, no aggro.<br>
<br>
If you camp out a rogue and cleric at the base of this stairway you can quickly CR from any wipeout.<br>
